TWO children were burnt to death while sleeping at Lwamondo-Khumbe Village outside Thohoyandou in Limpopo.Police spokesperson Colonel Moatshe Ngoepe said  it's alleged that the two children Rolivhuwa
Tshifaro (4)  and Ophunaho Tshifaro (3) were
left sleeping alone in a house in at Lwamondo-Khumbe village.He said members of the community noticed heavy smoke coming
out of the house where the children were sleeping and a huge flame of fire was coming
